Package: workflow-engine
Version: 7.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.27)
Maintainer: haozi <haozi@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/haozicnm/workflow-engine-desktop
Description: Workflow Engine standalone HTTP server
  A workflow automation engine with 14+ step types
  (HTTP, shell, file, Excel, browser, condition, loop, etc.).
  Provides REST API + Vue 3 web frontend via embedded axum server.
